<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc9d28123-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s390h–12p"><num value="390h–12p">§ 390h–12p.</num><heading> Tooele Wastewater Treatment and Reuse Project</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idc9d28124-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s390h–12p/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> Authorization</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary, in cooperation with Tooele City, Utah, is authorized to participate in the design, planning, and construction of the Tooele Wastewater Treatment and Reuse Project.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idc9d28125-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s390h–12p/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Cost share</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Federal share of the cost of a project described in subsection (a) shall not exceed 25 percent of the total cost.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idc9d28126-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s390h–12p/c"><num value="c" class="bold">(c)</num><heading class="bold"> Limitation</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall not provide funds for the operation or maintenance of a project described in subsection (a).</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idc9d28127-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/575/tXVI/s1630">Pub. L. 102–575, title XVI, § 1630</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/104/266/s2/a/2">Pub. L. 104–266, § 2(a)(2)</ref>, <date date="1996-10-09">Oct. 9, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/3294">110 Stat. 3294</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
